g.title: G00000
g.text: The system can operate within acceptable risk with respect to the specific accident Collision being caused by an adversary.

g.title: G00001
g.text: All potential hazards leading to Collision
have been identified with STAMP and the likelihood
of an attacker being able to cause them is acceptable.

g.title: G00008

or H1 cannot be caused by an adversary.
